name: AU REVOIR
description: Have you ever been to any place and loved it so much that when it was time to leave that place, you got upset. This picture is about a journey of a guy, who went to France and he was in so love with this country and it's people that when it was time to leave, he got little upset and sat all quiet in his room looking through the windows and wondering about those happy memories he made here. This picture is a feeling that every individual goes through atleast once in their life.
